</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">என்றால்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அது</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மிகையாகாது</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.</font></font></p>
