</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">என்ற</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கேள்விக்குச்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
