</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மூவொரு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இறைவனின்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">பெயரால்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஒன்றுசேர்க்கப்பட்டு</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">,
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இயேசுவின்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
