</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தலைமையின்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கீழ்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">வழிநடக்கின்ற</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அனைத்துலக</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இறைமக்களின்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">திருக்கூட்டம்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஆகும்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இந்த</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இறைமக்கள்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">திருக்கூட்டத்தோடு</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">,
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">பிற</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கிறிஸ்தவர்கள்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">,
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">பிற</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">சமயத்தினர்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">,
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஏன்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">எல்லா</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மக்களுமே</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">வெவ்வேறு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">வகைகளில்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தொடர்புடையவர்களே</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.</font></font></p>
<p align="justify" style="margin-bottom: 0.35cm; line-height: 115%"><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">திருச்சபையின்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நிர்வாக</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">முறைமைகளை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நெறிப்படுத்துகின்ற</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஏடாகிய</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
“</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">திருச்சபைச்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">சட்டத்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தொகுப்பு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">”
</font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">(Code
of Canon Law) </font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மறைமாவட்டத்தைக்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கீழ்வருமாறு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">வரையறுக்கிறது</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">:</font></font></p>
<p align="justify" style="margin-bottom: 0.35cm; line-height: 115%">”<font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN"><i>மறைமாவட்டம்
என்பது குருகுழாமின்
ஒத்துழைப்புடன் மேய்ப்புப்
பணிக்காக ஆயரிடம் ஒப்படைக்கப்பட்டுள்ள
இறை மக்களின் ஒரு பகுதியாகும்</i></span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><i>;
</i></font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN"><i>இவ்வாறு</i></span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><i>,
</i></font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN"><i>தன்
மேய்ப்பரோடு இணைந்து</i></span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><i>,
</i></font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN"><i>தூய
ஆவியில் நற்செய்தி</i></span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><i>,
</i></font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN"><i>நற்கருணை
வழியாக அவரால் ஒன்று கூட்டப்பட்டு
அது ஒரு தனித்திருச்சபையாக
உருப்பெறுகிறது</i></span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><i>;
</i></font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN"><i>அதில்
ஒரே</i></span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><i>,
</i></font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN"><i>தூய
கத்தோலிக்க</i></span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><i>,
</i></font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN"><i>திருத்தூதுவர்
திருச்சபை உண்மையாகவே உள்ளது</i></span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><i>;
</i></font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN"><i>செயலாற்றுகிறது</i></span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><i>”
</i></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><i>-
</i></font></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">(</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">திருச்சபைச்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">சட்டம்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">எண்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">369).
</font></font>
</p>
<p align="justify" style="margin-bottom: 0.35cm; line-height: 115%"><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">உலகத்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">திருச்சபையின்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தனிப்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
