<p align="justify" style="margin-bottom: 0.35cm; line-height: 115%"><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">	2)
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கோட்டாறு
