</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அவன்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">உறுதியாக</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இருந்தான்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அவனுக்கும்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அடிமேல்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அடிகொடுத்து</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அடிபணிய</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">வைக்க</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">முயன்றார்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அதிகாரி</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஆனால்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அருளப்பனோ</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">,
”</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">என்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">உடலை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">வேண்டுமென்றால்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நீர்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">துண்டுதுண்டு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஆக்கிவிடலாம்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஆனால்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">எனது</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஆன்மாவை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">என்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கடவுளிடமிருந்து</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நீர்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">பிரிக்கமுடியாது</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">”
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">என்று</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">வீரத்தோடு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">பதிலிறுத்தான்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
</font></font>
</p>
<p align="justify" style="margin-bottom: 0.35cm; line-height: 115%"><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தோல்வியுற்ற</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நீதிபதி</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கிறிஸ்தவர்களை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மறுநாளும்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அடித்துத்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">துன்புறுத்தி</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">,
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அவர்களுடைய</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">காயங்களில்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மிளகுப்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">பொடி</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தூவி</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">சித்திரவதை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">செய்து</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">பார்த்தான்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அவர்கள்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தங்கள்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கிறித்தவ</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நம்பிக்கையில்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">விடாப்பிடியாக</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இருந்ததைக்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கண்டு</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">,
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தன்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மேலதிகாரியான</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நாகம்பிள்ளை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">என்ற</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அரசு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நிர்வாகியிடம்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நடந்ததைக்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கூறினான்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கிறிஸ்தவ</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நாடார்களை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இம்சைப்படுத்திய</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">செய்தி</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">திருவிதாங்கூர்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மன்னரின்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">காதுகளுக்கு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">எட்டினால்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தனது</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">பெயர்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கெட்டுவிடுமே</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">என்று</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அஞ்சிய</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அரசு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நிர்வாகி</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நாகம்பிள்ளை</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">,
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அவசர</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அவசரமாக</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அந்த</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கிறிஸ்தவர்களைச்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">சிறையில்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அடைத்தான்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அவர்களுக்கு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஆறுதல்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கூறிட</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">திருவிதாங்கோடு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மறைத்தளத்தில்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">பணிபுரிந்த</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அலோசியுஸ்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஃபால்சான்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
