Falcao) </font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">என்ற</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஒரே</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஒரு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இயேசு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">சபைக்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">குரு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மட்டும்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இருந்தார்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
 </font></font>
</p>
<p align="justify" style="margin-bottom: 0.35cm; line-height: 115%"><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இந்த</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">வரலாற்றை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">எடுத்துரைத்த</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">பவுலீனுஸ்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தாம்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மறுநாள்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
