</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மரத்தில்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கட்டித்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தொங்கவிட்டு</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">,
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அடித்து</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நொறுக்கி</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">,
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அவன்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">தனது</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கிறிஸ்தவ</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">நம்பிக்கையைக்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கைவிட்டுவிட</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">வேண்டுமென்று</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கட்டாயப்படுத்தினார்கள்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">உயிர்நீத்த</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அருளப்பனின்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கல்லறையை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">இன்றும்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மாங்கோடு</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">-</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கோணத்துவிளையில்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">காணலாம்</span></font></font></span></font><font face="Latha, serif"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">.
</font></font><font face=""><span lang="ar-SA"><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">அருளப்பனை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">ஒரு</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">புனிதராகக்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">கருதி</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மக்கள்</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
</font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt"><span lang="ta-IN">மரியாதை</span></font></font><font face="Latha"><font size="2" style="font-size: 10pt">
